sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User / Data Scientist
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API Server<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant Webhook as Mutating Webhook<br/>9443/TCP HTTPS TLS
    participant Controller as RayCluster Controller
    participant Router as OpenShift Router<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant OAuth as OAuth Proxy Sidecar<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Dashboard as Ray Dashboard<br/>8265/TCP HTTP
    participant RayHead as Ray Head Node<br/>10001/TCP gRPC mTLS
    participant RayWorker as Ray Worker<br/>gRPC mTLS

    Note over User,RayWorker: Flow 1: RayCluster Creation on OpenShift

    User->>K8sAPI: POST RayCluster CR<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    K8sAPI->>Webhook: Mutate RayCluster<br/>TLS (self-signed certs)
    Webhook-->>K8sAPI: Inject oauth-proxy sidecar,<br/>mTLS init containers,<br/>CA volumes, TLS env vars
    K8sAPI-->>User: RayCluster Created

    Controller->>K8sAPI: Watch RayCluster events
    Controller->>K8sAPI: Create Route, Service, SA,<br/>Secret, NetworkPolicy<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount token

    Note over User,RayWorker: Flow 2: Ray Dashboard Access (OAuth)

    User->>Router: GET Ray Dashboard<br/>HTTPS/443 TLS (edge)
    Router->>OAuth: Forward request<br/>HTTPS/8443 TLS (reencrypt)
    OAuth->>OAuth: OpenShift OAuth authentication
    OAuth->>Dashboard: Proxy to dashboard<br/>HTTP/8265 plaintext (localhost)
    Dashboard-->>OAuth: Dashboard response
    OAuth-->>Router: Encrypted response
    Router-->>User: Dashboard HTML

    Note over User,RayWorker: Flow 3: RayClient mTLS Connection

    User->>Router: RayClient connect<br/>HTTPS/443 TLS passthrough
    Router->>RayHead: gRPC/10001<br/>mTLS (CA-signed certs)
    RayHead-->>User: gRPC response

    Note over User,RayWorker: Flow 4: Ray Cluster Internal (mTLS)

    RayWorker->>RayHead: gRPC/10001<br/>mTLS (CA-signed cert)
    RayHead->>RayWorker: Task distribution<br/>mTLS (CA-signed cert)
